channel.title: How do I host my own silab client?
channel.description:
Alrity, so uhm... When I download a silab based server with godswords and everything, I cant play it! I have the version 4 of silab How do I host my own server on silab? I know abbout No-Ip and dont redirect me to stickies cuz I've read every single sticky and none helps me. what i basically want, is to be able to make my own server abbout silab and mod it myself jsut the way I like it and be able to play it USING the silab items I'm sick of entering silab servers that suck!(for me) So, I wana make my own silab server, BUT HOW DO I PLAY IT ON MY OWN COMPUTER? Thank you :)
OMFG IM STARTING TO FREAK OUT! LISTEN UP GUYS! I have a server... I host it... everybody's happy! I have a silab server... I try to play it at "localhost" or "127.0.01"... BUT DOESNT WORKS!!! ffs read!
